        "html": "=<p>Dear {{$json.RecipientName}},</p>\n\n<p>We would like to inform you that a dependency blocking the task <b>{{$json.title}}</b> has been resolved.</p>\n\n<p><b>Task Details</b><br>\n* Task Title: {{$json.title}}<br>\n* Dependency Cleared On: {{$json.updated_at}}</p>\n\n<p>You may now proceed with execution as planned. Please update progress accordingly.</p>\n\n<p>Regards,<br>\n<b>Project Coordination Team</b></p>",
